NAME
       gnome-hint - show hint at Gnome startup.

SYNOPSIS
       gnome-hint  [   --browse-hints  ]   [   --browse-motd ]  [
       --browse-fortune ]  [  --session-login ]


DESCRIPTION
       gnome-hint allows you to show hint at Gnome  startup.  You
       can configure this in the control center.

OPTIONS
       --browse-hints
              Start in hint browsing mode.

       --browse-motd
              Start in motd mode.

       --browse-fortune
              Start in fortune mode.

       --session-login
              Start in session login mode (used from gsm).

